==English==
===Noun===
'''police officer'''

#An [[officer]] in a law enforcement agency.

====Usage note====
This term is [[gender-neutral]].  The [[gender-specific]] terms are ''[[policeman]]'' for a male police officer and ''[[policewoman]]'' for a female police officer.

